filter.doc: Filter search results. (string)Applicable values:- ebooks: All Google eBooks.- free-ebooks: Google eBook with full volume text viewability.- full: Public can view entire volume text.- paid-ebooks: Google eBooks with a price.- partial: Public able to see parts of text.
